<bibRefCitation id="806F5AE27B73FFC8FF7B3E369B192B26" author="Arce-Perez, R. &amp; Moron, M. A." box="[229,533,296,323]" pageId="13" pageNumber="580" pagination="23 - 27" refId="ref10716" refString="Arce-Perez, R. &amp; Moron, M. A. (2005) New species and new records of species of Macrodactylus Dejean (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae: Melolonthinae: Macrodactylini) from Honduras and Nicaragua. Zootaxa, 1012 (1), 23 - 27. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 1012.1.3" type="journal article" year="2005">Arce-Pérez &amp; Morón 2005</bibRefCitation>
